    "text": [
        "Dear Mr Jones,",
        "I am writing to inform about a business meeting on new business enhancement in March by TATA Company.",
        "The conference will give more information on technology which enable our business to the next level. It is scheduled by the major business development organization from Chennai.",
        "Last week, I was surfing  the internet to gain knowledge on a demand generation. Surprisingly, I noticed about this summit on the social media page, and I registered as an attendee on behalf of our company.",
        "It is very essential for me to participate in such event as a business leader. It will give new contact for our business and help others to know about our organization.",
        "I would be grateful if you allow me for attending this meeting and I would appreciate it ,If you could let me know the status by end of this week to make an arrangements.",
        "Yours Sincerely,",
        "Arun kumar"
    ],
